### Gateway health
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

### Search flights through gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/flights/search?origin=DEL&destination=BOM&departureDate={{departureDate}}&passengers=1

### Search mock GDS/Skyscanner through gateway
GET http://localhost:8080/api/flights/provider-search?origin=DEL&destination=BOM&departureDate={{departureDate}}&passengers=1

### Create booking through gateway
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "asha@example.com",
  "flightId": "SK101",
  "totalAmount": 1500.00,
  "currency": "INR",
  "passengers": [
    {
      "firstName": "Asha",
      "lastName": "Rao",
      "dateOfBirth": "1998-03-15",
      "passportNumber": "A1234567",
      "email": "asha@example.com"
    }
  ]
}

### Pay through gateway
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "asha@example.com",
  "amount": 1500.00,
  "currency": "INR",
  "paymentMethodToken": "pm_success"
}

### Send notification through gateway
POST http://localhost:8080/api/notifications
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": "{{bookingId}}",
  "userId": "asha@example.com",
  "recipient": "asha@example.com",
  "subject": "SkyWays booking confirmed",
  "body": "Your SkyWays booking has been confirmed."
}
